<div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span4">
        <h2>What it's about?</h2>

        <p>With OpenBacklog.org you can coordinate project development in an open manner: Create features with transparent discussion boards and involve your users and customers in the development process of the software they use and love.</p>
        <p>Manage your backlog and change priorities of user-stories and epics, let your users and developers vote on functionality and priorities.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="span4">
        <h2>Get the Code</h2>
        <p>The day OpenBacklog.org launches to the public the source will be publicly available for you to fork on <a href="http://github.com">github.com</a></p>.
    </div>
    <div class="span4">
        <h2>Take part</h2>
        <p>OpenBacklog.org will be one of the project backlogs hosted here for everyone to participate and shape the future-features of this site. Stay tuned!<p>
    </div>
</div>
